, 35, pp. 1051-1058; Klein, C., Morphological evidence of lake level changes, Western Shore of the Dead Sea (1982) Isr J Earth Sci, 31, pp. 67-94; Osetinsky, I., (2006) Climate changes over the E. Mediterranean-a synoptic systems classification approach, p. 138. , Ph. D. Thesis, University of Tel-Aviv; Saaroni, H., Ziv, B., Edelson, J., Alpert, P., Long-term variations in summer temperatures over the Eastern Mediterranean (2003) Geophys Res Lett, 30 (18), p. 1946. , doi:10.1029/2003GL017742; Stanhill, G., Changes in the rate of evaporation from the Dead Sea (1994) Int J Climatol, 14, pp. 465-471; Steinhorn, I., (1981) A hydro-graphical and physical study of the Dead Sea during the destruction of its long-term meromictic stratification, p. 323. , Ph. D. Thesis, Weizmann Institute of Science, Rehovot; Ziv, B., Saaroni, H., Baharad, A., Yekutieli, D., Alpert, P., Indications for aggravation in summer heat conditions over the Mediterranean basin (2005) Geophys Res Lett, 32, p. 12706. , doi:10.1029/2005GL022796","Alpert, P.; Department of Geophysics and Planetary Sciences, Tel Aviv University, Tel Aviv 69978, Israel; email: pinhas@cyclone.tau.ac.il",,,,,,,,01650009,,CLCHD,,"English","Clim. Change",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79952755519
